## üõ† **Tech Stack**  
- `transformers` + `peft` (LoRA finetuning)  
- `bitsandbytes` (4-bit quantization)  
- `React` (UI)   
- `FastAPI` (Backend)
- `Python` (Backend)
- `React.JS` (Frontend)
